Title : Aloísio Roque Oppermann
Text : '''Aloísio Roque Opperman''' (June 19, 1936 &ndash; April 26, 2014) was a [[Roman Catholic]] bishop.

Ordained to the priesthood in 1961, he was named bishop of the Diocese of Ituitaba, [[Brazil]], in 1983 and then coadjutor bishop of Campanha in 1988 succeeding as diocesan bishop in 1991. In 1996, Oppermann was named Archbishop of Uberaba and retired in 2012.<ref>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/bopp.html Aloisio Roque Oppermann]</ref>

